window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Chloe Jones is trying to put the scandal of leaving her Super Bowl legend fiancé at the altar behind her.</b></p> <p>There is no better way to escape than to turn her island honeymoon into a much-needed vacation with her girls. What she isn't expecting is to meet a hot stranger. Don't they say to get over someone you need to get under someone else?</p> <p>Chloe's ready for a fresh start. Shame her vengeful ex is making it difficult for her. That is until she lands the job of her dreams. She isn't expecting to come face to face with the hot stranger from her island escape—Noah Stone: New York's biggest playboy, and her new boss.</p> <p>Chloe can be professional, even if all she can think about is those lips. And the way he fills out his suit pants. He's totally off-limits, and she's signed the paperwork that says so.</p>"; 
